  ('medical-tech-moex-21070', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '由感染了第一型人類免疫缺乏病毒（HIV-1）的母親所產下之嬰兒，檢驗是否受到HIV-1的感染，下列方法 中，何者無法用來診斷？ 檢測HIV-1特異之IgG抗體  檢測p24抗原 聚合 連鎖反應（PCR）   病毒培養', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7e17c29d4088", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05e1b2825517", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 77, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-21071', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-093-0356504f', 'sub-medical-tech-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關第一型人類免疫缺乏病毒（HIV-1）的敘述，何者錯誤？ Tat蛋白質為一極強的轉活化因子（transactivator） 在複製的早期會產生多剪接的（multiple spliced）mRNA Rev蛋白質負責調控病毒蛋白質之表現 病毒之蛋白質 （protease）主要作用於細胞蛋白', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:17+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7e17c29d4088", "answer_pdf_sha1": "05e1b2825517", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093120", "c": "105", "s": "6001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血清免疫學與臨床病毒學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第二次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 78, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
